    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i feel like there’s nothing left inside. i used to see colors and shapes in everything, like the world was talking to me through the canvas. now it’s just... grey. silent. it’s like the part of me that actually lived, the part that mattered, just evaporated. i’m just a shape walking around, a hollow shell with no purpose.",
